Files containing the handler implementation(s) for articles.TagsAnonymousRegister

- articles/routers.go

Explanation
- I searched the codebase for the symbol TagsAnonymousRegister and found its definition in articles/routers.go.
- In that same file, TagsAnonymousRegister(router *gin.RouterGroup) registers GET "/" -> TagList, and the TagList(c *gin.Context) handler implementation is defined later in articles/routers.go.
- Therefore the handler(s) wired up by articles.TagsAnonymousRegister are implemented in articles/routers.go (path relative to the project root).
